records.nl_statement: Prove that two elements $a, b$ of a group generate the same subgroup as $b a b^2, b a b^3$.
records.lean_header:
import Mathlib

open Function Fintype Subgroup Ideal Polynomial Submodule Zsqrtd
open scoped BigOperators
records.ground_truth:
